biography_text: CISNEROS, Gil, a Representative from California; born in 1972; B.A., George Washington University, Washington, D.C.; M.B.A., Regis University, Denver, Colo.; M.A., Brown University, Providence, R.I., 2015; United States Navy, 1994-2004; corporate manager; non-profit executive; elected as a Democrat to the One Hundred Sixteenth Congress (January 3, 2019-present).
